{"tid":1296000,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【大行報告】大摩削其目標價至5元","createTime":"2019-07-08T08:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T03:49:38.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"96e919fa9eeb11c060bc80b9aba7c7132216fc05","tid":1296000,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"摩根士丹利發表研究報告，指吉利汽車(00175)近幾個月銷售增長惡化，今年首5個月總銷量僅達全年目標的37%，故將目標價由8元削減至5元，意味着其現價有近六成的潛在跌幅，續予其「減持」投資評級。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據該行的渠道調查，吉汽削減研發團隊25%及計劃減少2020年新款產品推出，相信其面對降低成本的壓力。該行認為，公司一直靠新產品保持盈利能力，此舉或影響其長遠前景。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該行預計吉汽上半年純利僅35億至36億元人民幣，按年跌幅46至48%，並下調其今年全年盈利預測39%至70億元人民幣，即按年跌44%。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該股周一(8日)隨大市向下，現跌4.1%報12.16元，成交額暫錄得逾8.7億元。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5e34b21653bedd5d3e52a7c95637d2ffc6a4636","tid":1296000,"uid":57308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:17:19.000Z","msg":"吉利主席仲在唔在生"},{"pid":"f35ccae43ad79ca9b5b47bd753c9b16f222d4dab","tid":1296000,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:17:46.000Z","msg":"繼續破產"},{"pid":"1e1a7e39ec5f9ad921001c2f1eed347a0751acc8","tid":1296000,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f35ccae43ad79ca9b5b47bd753c9b16f222d4dab","tid":1296000,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:17:46.000Z","msg":"繼續破產"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa8d010620dd28bddb88e05cb07344b32406a53","tid":1296000,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"但係係藍籌...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"